<section class="why-now" id="why-now">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Why This. Why Now.</div>
    <h2>The first-mover window closes in months, not years.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="why-now-grid">
    <div class="why-now-card reveal">
      <h3>
        The Companies That Deploy AI Operations in 2026 Will Define How the Industry Works
      </h3>
      <p>
        LLM-powered agents crossed the reliability threshold for healthcare
        operations in the last 18 months. The companies moving fastest aren't
        waiting for perfection — they're deploying now and compounding their
        operational advantage every month. By 2027, this will be table stakes.
        The advantage will belong to whoever moved first. If you're still
        evaluating, you're in a smaller group than you think.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-now-card reveal">
      <h3>The Second Wave Won't Wait for Stragglers</h3>
      <p>
        The first wave of digital health built point solutions. The second wave
        is building integrated care companies — and the ones launching now on
        AI-native infrastructure are arriving with the operational maturity
        their competitors will spend years trying to match. The wave doesn't
        pause. You're either on it or behind it.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-now-card reveal">
      <h3>Compliance Is Now a Startup Killer</h3>
      <p>
        HIPAA, SOC 2, state-level privacy laws — the regulatory surface area
        tripled in five years. No seed-stage company should be building this
        in-house. The ones that try burn 18 months and millions before seeing
        their first patient.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-now {
    padding: 8rem 4rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .why-now h2 {
    font-family: "DM Serif Display", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .why-now-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .why-now-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--slate));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.4s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .why-now-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.4),
      transparent
    );
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .why-now-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .why-now-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .why-now-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .why-now {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }
    .why-now-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
